<p>
This email is a confirmation that you approved <%=h @approval.approvable %> on
<%=h @approval.created_at.to_s :us_ordinal %>.  If you have any questions, please contact
<%=h @approval.approvable.contact_name %>
&lt;<a href="mailto:<%= @approval.approvable.contact_email%>"><%= @approval.approvable.contact_email %></a>&gt;.
</p>

<% if @approval.approvable_type == 'FundRequest' %>
<p>
With your approval, the request is locked so no additional changes will be permitted.
  <% if @approval.permitted_to?( :destroy, user: @approval.user ) %>
  At this time, you still have an opportunity to remove your approval.
  You may do so by visiting:
  &lt;<%=link_to polymorphic_url( @approval ), @approval %></a>&gt;
  <% end %>
</p>
<% end %>

